title: Standford Uni.- The roman army 284-1081
description:
FEUDALISM AND THE BATTLE OF MAZINKERT OPENED ANATOLIA TO A NEW
      ETHNOGRAPHIC MAP

      BEFORE THIS , A WAR MACHINE ACHIEVED THE MIRACLE OF KEEPING ALIVE
      FOR 1000 YEARS AN AGRARIAN STATE WITH NO ELECTRICITY , NO OIL AND NO
      DRONES

      THIS WAR MACHINE WAS THE ROMAN ARMY , AND HIS HISTORY DEMONSTRATES US
      THAT WAR IS NOT ONLY A MONEY AFFAIR , BUT ORGANIZATION AND

      "ESPRIT DE CORP"
